\lang1033\ldblquote And thirdly,\rdblquote  said Uncle Vernon, his mean little eyes now slits in his great purple face, \ldblquote we\rquote ve told Marge you attend St. Brutus\rquote s Secure Center for Incurably Criminal Boys.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
