\lang1033 Harry sat there, white-faced and furious, staring at Uncle Vernon, hardly able to believe it. Aunt Marge coming for a week-long visit \emdash  it was the worst birthday present the Dursleys had ever given him, including that pair of Uncle Vernon\rquote s old socks.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, Petunia,\rdblquote  said Uncle Vernon, getting heavily to his feet, \ldblquote I\rquote ll be off to the station, then. Want to come along for the ride, Dudders?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
