\lang1033\ldblquote See you in a bit, then,\rdblquote  he said, and he left the kitchen.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry, who had been sitting in a kind of horrified trance, had a sudden idea. Abandoning his toast, he got quickly to his feet and followed Uncle Vernon to the front door.\lang3081\par
