\lang1033 Harry tried to concentrate on his food, but his hands shook and his face was starting to burn with anger. \i Remember the form\i0 , he told himself. \i Think about Hogsmeade. Don\rquote t say anything. Don\rquote t rise\i0  \emdash\lang3081\par
