\lang1033\ldblquote Excellent,\rdblquote  said Fred, who had followed Harry through the por\-trait hole. \ldblquote I need to visit Zonko\rquote s. I\rquote m nearly out of Stink Pellets.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry threw himself into a chair beside Ron, his high spirits ebbing away. Hermione seemed to read his mind.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Harry, I\rquote m sure you\rquote ll be able to go next time,\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote They\rquote re bound to catch Black soon. He\rquote s been sighted once already\rdblquote\lang3081\par
