\lang1033\ldblquote Careful, Weasley, careful!\rdblquote  cried Professor Sprout as the beans burst into bloom before their very eyes.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 They had Transfiguration next. Harry, who had resolved to ask Professor McGonagall after the lesson whether he could go into\lang3081  \lang1033 Hogsmeade with the rest, joined the line outside the class trying to decide how he was going to argue his case. He was distracted, how\-ever, by a disturbance at the front of the line.\lang3081\par
