\lang1033\ldblquote Oh,\rdblquote  said Hermione. She paused again. Then \emdash\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Was Binky an \i old\i0  rabbit?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote N \emdash  no!\rdblquote  sobbed Lavender. \ldblquote H \emdash  he was only a baby!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Parvati tightened her arm around Lavender\rquote s shoulders.\lang3081\par
