\lang1033 Professor McGonagall opened the classroom door at that mo\-ment, which was perhaps lucky; Hermione and Ron were looking daggers at each other, and when they got into class, they seated themselves on either side of Harry and didn\rquote t talk to each other for the whole class.\lang3081\par
