\lang1033\ldblquote Ask her now,\rdblquote  Ron hissed at Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Oh, but \emdash\rdblquote  Hermione began.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Go for it, Harry,\rdblquote  said Ron stubbornly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry waited for the rest of the class to disappear, then headed nervously for Professor McGonagall\rquote s desk.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes, Potter?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry took a deep breath.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Professor, my aunt and uncle \emdash  er \emdash  forgot to sign my form,\rdblquote  he said.\lang3081\par
