\par
\lang1033 There was nothing to be done. Ron called Professor McGonagall a lot of names that greatly annoyed Hermione; Hermione assumed an \ldblquote all-for-the-best\rdblquote  expression that made Ron even angrier, and Harry had to endure everyone in the class talking loudly and hap\-pily about what they were going to do first, once they got into Hogsmeade.\lang3081\par
