\par
\lang1033 On Halloween morning, Harry awoke with the rest and went down to breakfast, feeling thoroughly depressed, though doing his best to act normally.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote We\rquote ll bring you lots of sweets back from Honeydukes,\rdblquote  said Hermione, looking desperately sorry for him.\lang3081\par
