\lang1033\ldblquote Password?\rdblquote  said the Fat Lady, jerking out of a doze.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Fortuna Major,\rdblquote  said Harry listlessly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 The portrait swung open and he climbed through the hole into the common room. It was full of chattering first and second years, and a few older students, who had obviously visited Hogsmeade so often the novelty had worn off.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Harry! Harry! Hi, Harry!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
