\lang1033 But Harry didn\rquote t go back to the common room; he climbed a staircase, thinking vaguely of visiting the Owlery to see Hedwig, and was walking along another corridor when a voice from inside one of the rooms said, \ldblquote Harry?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
