\lang1033\ldblquote With a little help from Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot, and Prongs,\rdblquote  Fred muttered in Harry\rquote s ear.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Only one person wasn\rquote t joining in the festivities. Hermione, in\-credibly, was sitting in a corner, attempting to read an enormous book entitled \i Home Life and Social Habits of British Muggles.\i0  Harry broke away from the table where Fred and George had started jug\-gling butterbeer bottles and went over to her.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Did you even come to the match?\rdblquote  he asked her.\lang3081\par
