\lang1033\ldblquote Nonsense!\rdblquote  said Percy, looking startled. \ldblquote You had too much to eat, Ron \emdash  had a nightmare \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m telling you \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
