\lang1033\ldblquote Oh,\rdblquote  said Ron, looking slightly put out.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 The first thing they saw on entering Hagrid\rquote s cabin was Buck\-beak, who was stretched out on top of Hagrid\rquote s patchwork quilt, his enormous wings folded tight to his body, enjoying a large plate of dead ferrets. Averting his eyes from this unpleasant sight, Harry saw a gigantic, hairy brown suit and a very horrible yellow-and-orange tie hanging from the top of Hagrid\rquote s wardrobe door.\lang3081\par
