\lang1033\ldblquote Hagrid, we should\rquote ve helped as well \emdash  sorry \emdash\rdblquote  Harry began awkwardly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m not blamin\rquote  yeh!\rdblquote  said Hagrid, waving Harry\rquote s apology aside. \ldblquote Gawd knows yeh\rquote ve had enough ter be gettin\rquote  on with. I\rquote ve seen yeh practicin\rquote  Quidditch ev\rquote ry hour o\rquote  the day an\rquote  night \emdash  but I gotta tell yeh, I thought you two\rquote d value yer friend more\rquote n broom\-sticks or rats. Tha\rquote s all.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry and Ron exchanged uncomfortable looks.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Really upset, she was, when Black nearly stabbed yeh, Ron. She\rquote s got her heart in the right place, Hermione has, an\rquote  you two not talkin\rquote  to her \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
