\lang1033\ldblquote Enough of this,\rdblquote  said Lupin, and there was a steely note in his voice Harry had never heard before. \ldblquote There\rquote s one certain way to prove what really happened. Ron, \i give me that rat.\i0\rdblquote\lang3081\par
