\lang1033 Harry sat down in his vacated chair, staring glumly at the floor. He heard the door close and looked up. Dumbledore was still there.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Why so miserable, Harry?\rdblquote  he said quietly. \ldblquote You should be very proud of yourself after last night.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
