\lang1033 Dumbledore looked mildly impressed.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Do you know, Harry, I think she might have been,\rdblquote  he said thoughtfully. \ldblquote Who\rquote d have thought it? That brings her total of real predictions up to two. I should offer her a pay raise. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote But \emdash\rdblquote  Harry looked at him, aghast. How could Dumbledore take this so calmly?\lang3081\par
