\lang1033 Harry couldn\rquote t imagine when that would be. Dumbledore looked as though he knew what Harry was thinking.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I knew your father very well, both at Hogwarts and later, Harry,\rdblquote  he said gently. \ldblquote He would have saved Pettigrew too, I am sure of it.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry looked up at him. Dumbledore wouldn\rquote t laugh \emdash  he could tell Dumbledore \'85\lang3081\par
